metadata.name: African Masks #1
metadata.description:
The African Mask Collection is created by Denise Mythic, an Congolese artiste living in Belgium. She's the first official New Breed Gallery resident artiste who let's her whole collection and artworks be curated through New Breed Gallery.

She was discovered in a youth art project and was rapidly noticed because of the colors she used, the intricate details and a very unique style of drawing and contemporary art use.

The whole collection is based on African Masks and African culture.
